title: Casual Game Music Loops Vol. 2
description: 20 high quality and ready to use music loops
longDescription:
A collection of 20 high quality and ready to use music loops. It features loops for different gameplay scenarios, menus and stages. The moods and ambiances of the tracks vary from melancholic, sci-fi and medieval to happy, casual and positive.


All tracks are .wav 44.1kHz 16-bit Stereo.
